- "inclusivity of wheelchair accessibility" indicates that the business is wheelchair accessible.

- "Struggling businesses" refers to businesses with a rating below 3 stars;
- "Keepers of the flame" refers to the current managers;
- "Swipe of a card" refers to the business accepting credit cards;
- "Wheels of a chair" refers to the business being wheelchair accessible.

